Package acdc.TreeDataModel

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    File1
    File1 is the class representing the data model of the tree I choose to implement my own data model and not DefaultMutableTreeNode when I try to build a json cache.
    FileTreeCellRenderer
    FileTreeCellRenderer is a custom implementation of DefaultTreeCellRenderer It is used to modify the icon of empty file that are showed as leaf.
    FileTreeModel
    FileTreeModel is a custom implementation of TreeModel It is useful to create my own data structure that is represented by the File1 class.
